# id: AbstractSpanDecorator -> public static String stripSchemeAndOptions(Endpoint endpoint)
commentText: This method removes the scheme, any leading slash characters and_options from the supplied URI. This is intended to extract a meaningful_name from the URI that can be used in situations, such as the operation_name.__@param endpoint The endpoint_@return The stripped value from the URI
codeText: public static String stripSchemeAndOptions(Endpoint endpoint) {_        int start = endpoint.getEndpointUri().indexOf(':')__        start++__        _        while (endpoint.getEndpointUri().charAt(start) == '/') {_            start++__        }_        int end = endpoint.getEndpointUri().indexOf('?')__        return end == -1 ? endpoint.getEndpointUri().substring(start)_                : endpoint.getEndpointUri().substring(start, end)__    }
